♪In the dream♪

275
00:24:31,695 --> 00:24:35,712
♪Singing my yearning♪

276
00:24:40,084 --> 00:24:41,163
I'm an old person.

277
00:24:42,603 --> 00:24:43,923
I will need you to take care of me.

278
00:24:46,403 --> 00:24:47,203
Okay.

279
00:24:48,843 --> 00:24:49,724
